side%20an%20aluminum%20block.%20It%E2%80%99s%20slower%20to%20heat%20up%20(about%2030%20to%2060%20seconds)%20and%20less%20efficient%20than%20ThermoJet%2C%20but%20it%20still%20offers%20decent%20thermal%20stability%20for%20home%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20boilers%20heat%20a%20full%20reservoir%20of%20water%20and%20take%20longer%20to%20warm%20up%2C%20but%20they%20offer%20greater%20thermal%20stability%2C%20especially%20when%20pulling%20back-to-back%20shots%20or%20steaming%20milk.%20A%20single%20boiler%20machine%20uses%20the%20same%20boiler%20to%20heat%20water%20for%20both%20brewing%20and%20steaming%2C%20which%20means%20you%20can%20only%20do%20one%20at%20a%20time.%20After%20pulling%20a%20shot%2C%20you%20have%20to%20wait%20a%20few%20seconds%20for%20the%20machine%20to%20come%20to%20temperature%20before%20steaming%20milk%20(or%20vice%20versa).%20A%20dual%20boiler%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20separate%20boilers%20for%20each%20task%2C%20so%20you%20can%20brew%20and%20steam%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20do%20Breville%20espresso%20machines%20typically%20last%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20regular%20maintenance%2C%20Breville%20espresso%20machines%20typically%20last%205%20to%2010%20years.%20All%20models%20come%20with%20a%20minimum%201-year%20warranty%20(most%20have%202%20years)%2C%20and%20replacement%20parts%20are%20available%20for%20repairs.%20Machines%20like%20the%20Dual%20Boiler%2C%20which%20are%20more%20modular%20and%20serviceable%2C%20may%20last%20even%20longer%20with%20proper%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20maintenance%20is%20required%20for%20Breville%20machines%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20backflush%20your%20machine%20regularly%20(with%20the%20included%20cleaning%20disc)%2C%20purge%20and%20wipe%20down%20the%20steam%20wand%20after%20every%20use%2C%20and%20run%20the%20built-in%20descaling%20cycle%20periodically%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20water%20hardness.%20Breville%20includes%20descaling%20solution%20and%20other%20cleaning%20tools%20with%20most%20models%2C%20and%20even%20entry-level%20machines%20come%20with%20clear%20instructions%20to%20help%20keep%20everything%20running%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20Breville%20espresso%20machines%20good%20for%20beginners%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20Breville%20machines%20are%20designed%20with%20accessibility%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20many%20models%2C%20like%20the%20Barista%20Express%20Impress%20and%20Oracle%20Jet%2C%20offer%20guided%20workflows%20and%20automation%20to%20help%20beginners%20brew%20great%20espresso%20with%20minimal%20trial%20and%20error.%20Even%20the%20more%20manual%20models%20like%20the%20Bambino%20are%20easy%20to%20set%20up%20and%20come%20with%20all%20the%20tools%20you%20need%20to%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20I%20get%20a%20single%20or%20dual%20boiler%20model%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20home%20users%2C%20Breville%E2%80%99s%20ThermoJet%20and%20Thermocoil%20machines%20are%20more%20than%20enough%3B%20they%20just%20require%20a%20quick%20wait%20when%20switching%20between%20brewing%20and%20steaming.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20steam%20milk%20and%20brew%20at%20the%20same%20time%20or%20fine-tune%20your%20shot%20with%20more%20precision%2C%20the%20Dual%20Boiler%20is%20worth%20the%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-breville-espresso-machine%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753301497000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6881380885e81483682e8e1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-breville-espresso-machine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20waded%20through%20Breville's%2011%20espresso%20machines%20to%20find%20the%20best%20options%20for%20beginners%2C%20advanced%20users%2C%20and%20those%20who%20only%20want%20to%20spend%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abbychersh%40gmail.com%20(A